Kubernetes - POD/Node Scalability

Horizantal Pod Auto Scaling 

Example in Replicaset and Deployment YAML the replicas:3 the number which you gave is understand by controller inside kubernetes for self healing so will mainatain same number 

But in case of HPA controller will actually monitor the load and control the replicas set 



