BY Default Deployment controller replica are static it wont change count dynamically along with load
TO make Dynamic this replicas we need to integrate HOrizantal pod autoscaler .

So HPA monitor load as given set point it will update replicas accordinlgy into deployment controller 
-------------------------------
HPA YAML 

apiVersion: autoscaling/v2
kind: HorizontalPodAutoscaler
metadata:
  name: nginx
spec:
  scaleTargetRef:
    apiVersion: apps/v1
    kind: Deployment
    name: nginx-hpa
  minReplicas: 1
  maxReplicas: 10
  metrics:
  - type: Resource
    resource:
      name: cpu
      target:
        type: Utilization
        averageUtilization: 1

-----------------------------------
Deployment YAML 

apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: nginx-hpa
  namespace: default
spec:
  replicas: 1
  selector:
    matchLabels:
      app: nginx
  template:
    metadata:
      labels:
        app: nginx
    spec:
      containers:
      - name: nginx
        image: nginx:1.7.9
        ports:
        - containerPort: 80
        resources:
          # You must specify requests for CPU to autoscale
          # based on CPU utilization
          requests:
            cpu: "250m"
