Just compare 3 yamls and find the major diff 

Trget reference will be same in deployment yaml and hpa yaml 


How about target specifications 
example t2.micro 1 cpu is capacity

so for pod we are not having size right 

sowe are giving specifications like 
        resources:
          # You must specify requests for CPU to autoscale
          # based on CPU utilization
          requests:
            cpu: "250m"

so total 250millcore for the pod capacity load

so set point here is 
      target:
        type: Utilization
        averageUtilization: 1


means 1*250/100 set point reached them immediately so 2.5% reached so immediately the values of replicas will be set by min and max replica based on the load in HPA controller 


